         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head>
            <p>Year 3, Neikandros <supplied reason="subaudible">son</supplied> of Neikagoras [ . . . ] aged 40. </p>
            <p>Year 6, Sara,  <supplied reason="subaudible">daughter</supplied> of Neikandros, Choiak 1 <note>November 27</note>, aged 17, full of  virtue.</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>The name Sara suggests a Jewish family</p>
            <p>l.6 Choiak 1 (November 27) </p>
            <p>l.7 The comment is a very rare feature in Cyrenaican funerary inscriptions.</p>
         </div>
         
